      <title>RabbitMq安装(Windwos)</title>
      <link href="/2020/08/09/RabbitMq%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85(Windows)/"/>
      <url>/2020/08/09/RabbitMq%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85(Windows)/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="RabbitMq安装-Windwos"><a href="#RabbitMq安装-Windwos" class="headerlink" title="RabbitMq安装(Windwos)"></a>RabbitMq安装(Windwos)</h1><a id="more"></a><h2 id="安装前须知"><a href="#安装前须知" class="headerlink" title="安装前须知"></a>安装前须知</h2><p>由于RabbitMQ的安装需要依赖erlang的，所以在安装RabbitMQ前应该先安装erlang。但是RabbitMQ的版本与erlang的版本必须一致，具体可以查看此处:<a href="https://www.rabbitmq.com/which-erlang.html">具体说明</a></p><h2 id="ErLang安装"><a href="#ErLang安装" class="headerlink" title="ErLang安装"></a>ErLang安装</h2><ul><li><p>ErLang下载:<a href="https://www.erlang.org/downloads">下载链接</a></p></li><li><p>安装教程：很简单一路next即可。</p><h2 id="RabbitMQ安装"><a href="#RabbitMQ安装" class="headerlink" title="RabbitMQ安装"></a>RabbitMQ安装</h2></li><li><p>RabbitMQ官网下载地址:<a href="https://www.rabbitmq.com/download.html">下载链接</a><br>由于官网下载速度过慢，建议用此链接下载:<a href="https://dl.bintray.com/rabbitmq/all/rabbitmq-server/">快速链接</a></p></li><li><p>安装教程：so easy.一路next即可。</p><h2 id="配置RabbitMQ"><a href="#配置RabbitMQ" class="headerlink" title="配置RabbitMQ"></a>配置RabbitMQ</h2></li><li><p>启动 rabbitmq_management<br>用cmd进入到安装RabbitMQ的目录的sbin:    </p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">D:\Program Files (x86)\rabbitmq_server-3.8.3\sbin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>执行以下命令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">abbitmq-plugins <span class="built_in">enable</span> rabbitmq_management</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>执行成功如下：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">D:\Program Files (x86)\rabbitmq_server-3.8.3\sbin&gt;rabbitmq-plugins <span class="built_in">enable</span> rabbitmq_management</span><br><span class="line">Enabling plugins on node rabbit@DESKTOP-KK65UV4:</span><br><span class="line">rabbitmq_management</span><br><span class="line">The following plugins have been configured:</span><br><span class="line">  rabbitmq_management</span><br><span class="line">  rabbitmq_management_agent</span><br><span class="line">  rabbitmq_web_dispatch</span><br><span class="line">Applying plugin configuration to rabbit@DESKTOP-KK65UV4...</span><br><span class="line">The following plugins have been enabled:</span><br><span class="line">  rabbitmq_management</span><br><span class="line">  rabbitmq_management_agent</span><br><span class="line">  rabbitmq_web_dispatch</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">started 3 plugins.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>验证是否安装成功，在浏览器中访问该链接:<a href="localhost:15672">成功</a>，如下图：<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200510151255978.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3FxXzM4MTg3Mzg1,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center" alt="RabbitMQ登录页面"></p>]]></content>
      
      
