      <title>Ubuntun14.04安装MySQL5.7</title>
      <link href="/2020/08/09/Ubuntun14-04%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85MySQL5.7/"/>
      <url>/2020/08/09/Ubuntun14-04%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85MySQL5.7/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Ubuntun14-04安装MySQL5-7"><a href="#Ubuntun14-04安装MySQL5-7" class="headerlink" title="Ubuntun14.04安装MySQL5.7"></a>Ubuntun14.04安装MySQL5.7</h2><a id="more"></a><h3 id="准备环境"><a href="#准备环境" class="headerlink" title="准备环境"></a>准备环境</h3><ol><li><p>查看系统版本下载相对应的mysql版本</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">uname -a 或者 lsb_release -a</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>下载对应的版本<a href="https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/file/?id=471390">mysq5.7.19</a>,下载完成后将MySQL安装包上传的到服务器</p></li></ol><h3 id="开始安装"><a href="#开始安装" class="headerlink" title="开始安装"></a>开始安装</h3><ol><li><p>切换为root权限</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">su root</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>更新资源</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">   sudo apt-get update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get upgrade</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>cd到放置mysql安装包的路径将该包解压</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">   <span class="built_in">cd</span> xxx</span><br><span class="line">tar -xvf mysql-server_5.7.19-1ubuntu14.04_amd64.deb-bundle.tar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>解压完之后一共应该有11个压缩包，按照一定顺序安装，顺序如下：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">   sudo dpkg -i mysql-common_5.7.19-1ubuntu14.04_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line">   sudo dpkg -i libmysqlclient20_5.7.19-1ubuntu14.04_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line">   sudo dpkg -i libmysqlclient-dev_5.7.19-1ubuntu14.04_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line">   sudo dpkg -i libmysqld-dev_5.7.19-1ubuntu14.04_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line">   sudo apt-get install libaio1</span><br><span class="line">   sudo dpkg -i mysql-community-client_5.7.19-1ubuntu14.04_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line">   sudo dpkg -i mysql-client_5.7.19-1ubuntu14.04_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line">   sudo dpkg -i mysql-community-source_5.7.19-1ubuntu14.04_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line">   sudo apt-get install libmecab2</span><br><span class="line">sudo dpkg -i mysql-community-server_5.7.19-1ubuntu14.04_amd64.deb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>按照如上步骤不出意外应该是能成功安装完成，在安装过程中会弹出一个界面让你输入密码，切记要记住自己输入的密码；安装完默认MySQL已经启动了，如果想查看是否已经启动可以通过如下命令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">service mysql status</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>默认情况下MySQL是不支持远程连接的，所以需要修改一些配置，具体命令如下</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">   <span class="built_in">cd</span> /etc/mysql/mysql.conf.d</span><br><span class="line">vim mysqld.cnf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将bind-address =127.0.0.1改为0.0.0.0即可，保存</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">   grant all privileges on *.* to <span class="string">&#x27;root&#x27;</span>@<span class="string">&#x27;%&#x27;</span> identified by <span class="string">&#x27;密码&#x27;</span> with grant option;</span><br><span class="line">flush privileges;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重新启动mysql.</p></li><li><p>MySQL启动或停止或重启命令</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">   service mysql start    ---启动</span><br><span class="line">   service mysql stop     ---停止</span><br><span class="line">   service mysql restart  ---重启</span><br><span class="line">service mysql status   ---查看状态</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
